title: Hot Dogs, Peanuts and Saints Baseball!...renovated 1 BR has it all!
posting_body: ['Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a guided tour today!', 'Smell the smells and hear the crack of the bat,  the roar of the crowd from CHS Field--Enjoy the fireworks following the SAINTS game!!', ' Get a start on your summer tan while enjoying life in this fabulous one bedroom with all new cabinets and stainless steel appliances--granite counter-tops--in the heart of ST Paul!', 'Catch the bus from your front door--.', '  This South-facing spacious one bedroom apartment features  big bright windows--bringing in natural light, large closet spaces, and plenty of cabinets !', '-and the view of Mears Park is stunning!', 'Get a work out in using our 24/7 private Fitness Center and Studio, relax in our indoor heated pool and get toasty warm in our sauna.', 'Mears Park Place is owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Conveniently located in trendy Lowertown across from Mears Park, you can walk the skyway down to the river and bike along the Bike trails through the city parks.', 'We are just 2 blocks from Union Depot and the light rail station, which can take you through St. Paul and connects to Minneapolis and the University campus, as well as the airport.', 'Mears Park Place Apartments features:', '* Indoor Pool', '* Sun Patio', '*', 'Rec Room', '* Sauna', '* Tanning Bed', '* Party Room', '* 24hr gym with fitness studio', '* Underground Parking', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule your guided tour today!', '(Tell them you saw #718 on Craigslist!)', '*Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
